data.description: Enjoy the comfort and convenience of this charming one story home that did not flood! This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, with plenty of space for your family and guests. The large den has vaulted ceilings and a wood burning fireplace, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan connects the den with the dining area, which can accommodate both casual and formal dining. The kitchen has ample cabinets and counter space, making it easy to prepare your favorite meals. The bedrooms are generous in size, with the master bedroom having its own private bathroom. The backyard is spacious and fenced, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. The home is also walking distance to the elementary school, adding to its convenience. Don't miss this opportunity to own this lovely home that has been well maintained by its owners!
